<item>
            <title>[LU-7509] Failover: recovery-random-scale test_fail_client_mds: /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 failed to initialize!</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7509</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/cfb6c466-9329-11e5-8070-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/cfb6c466-9329-11e5-8070-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_fail_client_mds failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 failed to initialize!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Update not seen after 90s: wanted &apos;&apos; got &apos;lustre:MDT0000&apos;
 recovery-random-scale test_fail_client_mds: @@@@@@ FAIL: /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 failed to initialize! 

Dumping lctl log to /logdir/test_logs/2015-11-24/lustre-master-el7-x86_64--failover--1_12_1__3252__-70314916677740-150435/recovery-random-scale.test_fail_client_mds.*.1448423529.log
CMD: shadow-52vm3,shadow-52vm4,shadow-52vm7,shadow-52vm8 /usr/sbin/lctl dk &amp;gt; /logdir/test_logs/2015-11-24/lustre-master-el7-x86_64--failover--1_12_1__3252__-70314916677740-150435/recovery-random-scale.test_fail_client_mds.debug_log.\$(hostname -s).1448423529.log;
         dmesg &amp;gt; /logdir/test_logs/2015-11-24/lustre-master-el7-x86_64--failover--1_12_1__3252__-70314916677740-150435/recovery-random-scale.test_fail_client_mds.dmesg.\$(hostname -s).1448423529.log
shadow-52vm4: open /proc/sys/lnet/dump_kernel failed: No such file or directory
shadow-52vm4: open(dump_kernel) failed: No such file or directory
shadow-52vm7: open /proc/sys/lnet/dump_kernel failed: No such file or directory
shadow-52vm7: open(dump_kernel) failed: No such file or directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Seems to be related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7499&quot; title=&quot;replay-vbr test_1b: /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 failed to initialize!&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7499&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7499&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
